## handoff
- produced: Playwright live-test of https://michaelwegter.com/demos/ai-chatbot-for-customer-support/ and admin panel; all critical paths verified
- decisions: portfolio 404 is expected GH Pages SPA behavior (not a failure); WASM model load delay in headless accepted per handoff instructions
- next needs: media-capture should load demo URL directly (not portfolio route) to avoid SPA redirect delay; allow 5-8s after load for model init before interacting
- risks: WASM model init time (~5-15s) means very fast test scripts will hit disabled-textarea; order lookup and FAQ flows unconfirmed (template-RAG fallback OK)

VERDICT: pass
